title: No. 4 Tech blanks K-State, 14-0 - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 4 Tech blanks K-State, 14-0 - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – No. 4 Texas Tech clinched its series in shutout fashion on Saturday, defeating Kansas State 14-0 at Rip Griffin Park. The series win marks the Red Raiders' third Big 12 series win in three tries to start the 2022 season.
